@startuml external-api-flow
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #f5f5f5

title 외부 API 연동 흐름 (OpenFeign 사용)\n예시: POST /api/v1/auth/send-code (SMS 인증코드 발송)

actor Client
participant "AuthController" as Controller
participant "AuthService" as Service
participant "SmsCodeRepository" as Repository
database "Database" as DB
participant "SmsProvider\n<<interface>>" as SmsProvider
participant "CoolSmsClient\n(OpenFeign)" as FeignClient
participant "CoolSMS API" as CoolSMS

Client -> Controller: POST /api/v1/auth/send-code\n{ phoneNumber, role }

Controller -> Service: sendCode(SendCodeReqDto)

Service -> Service: 발송 횟수 조회 및 30분 차단 여부 확인
Service -> Repository: findByPhoneNumber(phoneNumber)
Repository -> DB: SELECT
DB --> Repository: SmsCode (or empty)
Repository --> Service: Optional<SmsCode>

Service -> Service: SmsCode Entity 생성/갱신\n(인증코드 생성, 만료시각 설정)
Service -> Repository: save(SmsCode)
Repository -> DB: INSERT/UPDATE
DB --> Repository: SmsCode (saved)
Repository --> Service: SmsCode

Service -> SmsProvider: send(phoneNumber, code)

note over SmsProvider
  인터페이스 — 실제 구현체는
  MockSmsProvider 또는
  CoolSmsSmsProvider
end note

SmsProvider -> FeignClient: CoolSmsRequest
FeignClient -> CoolSMS: HTTP POST /messages
CoolSMS --> FeignClient: CoolSmsResponse
FeignClient --> SmsProvider: CoolSmsResponse
SmsProvider --> Service: (완료)

Service -> Service: Entity → SendCodeRespDto 변환
Service --> Controller: SendCodeRespDto

Controller --> Client: 200 OK\n{ "success": true, "data": SendCodeRespDto }

@enduml
